  "Description": {
    "English": "A curious mesh of old and new technology, a hybrid between two entirely separate methods of creation. Nonetheless, this <span class=\"name name-stellar\">location tracing device</span> appears fully functional.<br><br>Select this device and use <VAL_ON>Resonate (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to trace its harmonic origin.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "新旧科技的独特融合，其中混合着两种截然不同的制作工艺。无论如何，这台<span class=\"name name-stellar\">定位装置</span>似乎能够正常运作。<br><br>选择此装置并使用<VAL_ON>共鸣（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）<>追踪最初的谐波来源。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "由新舊科技結合而成的古怪產物，混合了兩種截然不同的創造方法。即使如此，這個<span class=\"name name-stellar\">地點追蹤裝置</span>看起來功能完全正常。<br><br>選擇本裝置並使用<VAL_ON>共振 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> 即可追蹤和諧來源。"
  },
